\begin_layout Standard
All analysis was performed on Matlab using custom scripts.
 All traces were exported as .swc files from TrakEM2.
 All tree lengths was reported as pathlengths unless noted otherwise.
 Similarly, all lengths to a pre or post synaptic site was reported as pathlengt
hs.
